<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Confirmar Exclusão</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #333;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    button, a {
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 10px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    button {
      background-color: #dc3545; /* Vermelho para botão de exclusão */
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #c82333;
    }

    a {
      background-color: #007bff; /* Azul para botão de cancelar */
    }

    a:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Confirmar Exclusão</h1>
  <p>Você tem certeza de que deseja excluir o livro <%= book.title %>?</p>
  <form action="/books/delete/<%= book.id %>" method="POST">
    <button type="submit">Confirmar Exclusão</button>
    <a href="/books">Cancelar</a>
  </form>
</body>
</html>
